<L>__{interior ben's room night}
<A>__{ben, dressed differently again, sits in a chair by his desk. he is writing. on the piece of paper is written: dear elaine, elaine, elaine, elaine, and her name several dozen times. he stops and looks up.}
<T>__{dissolve to:}
<L>__{interior braddock kitchen day}
<A>__{it is early morning. we see a swinging door pushed open to reveal: mr. braddock, dressed in a bathrobe, standing at the kitchen counter by the window through which we can see an orange tree. mr. braddock is pouring orange juice from a minute maid container. ben stands inside door.}
